    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Small cylindrical or flat bottles used to contain snuff, often carried on the person. Often highly decorative and made of a variety of materials. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
